Feature: User should be able to select skills

Scenario Outline: Should be able to add multiple skills
    Given: User select a skill
    When: User selectes another skill from the dropdown the page
    Then: User should be able to add another skill to input

Scenario Outline: No skill should be selected on page refreshing
    Given: User select a skill
    When: User refreshes the page
    Then: User shouldn't be able to see any skill selected


Scenario Outline: Should be able to remove selected skill from input field
    Given: User select some skill
    When: User try to remove slected skill
    Then: User should be able to remove skill from input    